mongo db

-- Linux:

how to connect to the mongo db:
mongosh

start mongodb start service:
sudo systemctl start mongod


install mongob:
sudo dpkg -i mongodb-org-server_7.0.1_amd64.deb


check mongobd status in linux:
sudo systemctl status mongod


install mongo shell:
sudo dpkg -i mongodb-mongosh_1.10.6_amd64.deb

install mongo compass:
sudo dpkg -i mongodb-compass_1.39.4_amd64.deb




-Linux mint shortcuts:

show active Windows shortcut: control + Windows + arrow down

